OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778440270
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman stabbed to death
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) have
OL,7,Farrested an 18-year-old man on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murder. He remains in
OL,9,Fcustody for questioning.
OL,11,FGMP have appealed for anyone with
OL,12,Finformation to contact them and say
OL,13,Fthe victim's family are being
OL,14,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
