PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778440270
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman stabbed to death
OL,6,F"We understand this is a deeply
OL,7,Fconcerning incident, and we will have
OL,8,Fextra patrols in the area. I encourage
OL,9,Fanyone with concerns or queries to
OL,10,Fplease speak with our teams.
OL,12,F"Scenes remain in place and our
OL,13,Fofficers will work throughout the day
OL,14,Fto conduct their investigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
